description: This source file implements platform-dependent and general utility functions for the Http Webs Session Object, specifically providing a function to create a new Webs Session object (HttpCreateWebsSession). The file includes licensing information, author details, and a function that internally calls HttpWssoCreate to instantiate the session object.

methods.name: ANSC_HANDLE HttpCreateWebsSession(ANSC_HANDLE hContainerContext,ANSC_HANDLE hOwnerContext,ANSC_HANDLE hAnscReserved)
methods.description: Creates a new HTTP Webs Session object by calling HttpWssoCreate with provided context handles.
